{"tid":2168264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國駐華大使強調英方認為「港獨」非解決香港問題選項","createTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T01:16:22.000Z","uid":70063,"like":18,"dislike":220,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"e932fd45023d374d4bee9f129e622a7ef77f8633","tid":2168264,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544780-20200820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544780-20200820.htm&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=c8d08d4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544780-20200820.htm&h=20970466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544780-20200820.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n即將離任的英國駐華大使吳百納舉行記者會，強調英方認為「港獨」絕非解決香港問題的選項，並譴責任何形式的暴力。<br />\n<br />\n吳百納說，英國希望見到香港的繁榮與穩定，但她拒絕正面回應英方將會如何處理前香港眾志創黨主席羅冠聰等人，據報有意在英國成立「流亡議會」。<br />\n<br />\n吳百納承認，英國確實擔憂「港區國安法」是否會動搖香港的高度自治與權利自由，但中英雙方在對待這些分歧上，溝通渠道一直暢通，相信問題最終可以透過對話解決，英國亦願意與中國深化合作，認為在非洲、第四次工業革命、氣候變化等議題上，中國仍然會是英國的密切夥伴。"},{"pid":"e36e154388fd584421d0f13eb119d343f4f43049","tid":2168264,"uid":104804,"like":76,"dislike":5,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"即將離任的英國駐華大使"},{"pid":"070ca7bc4236e16c0433a3d0f1dc895be59a02f3","tid":2168264,"uid":79117,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"751086e8d4a7a6112c80bcb5161230ef1bc76d9b","tid":2168264,"uid":38982,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"係人地方梗係講鬼話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e863903933d9a2ac4ed1be0386ce626e12429391","tid":2168264,"uid":273703,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:37:31.000Z",